Install fabric (apt-get install fabric)
Help from autoinstaller:
cd to source directory (which contains fabfile.py) and then read

fab help
fab prerequirements

====================================================
Prerequirements on server side (side of this script):
apt-get install sqlite3
sqlite3 status.db
sqlite> .exit

Prerequirements for continoue deploy:
install debian / ubuntu
install ssh server (apt-get install openssh-server)
sshkeygen ...
cd ~/.ssh
mv id_rsa.pub authorized_keys
scp id_rsa to fabric server
rm id_rsa
===================================================

See examples in fabfile.py for deployment

